query searchFilter($input: SearchFilterInput!, $paginate: Int!, $limit: Int!) {
   searchFilter(input: $input, paginate: $paginate, limit: $limit) {
       currentPage
       totalPages
       totalItems
       events {
           id
           categoryType
           name
           subcategories
           image
           city
           placeAddress
           latitude
           longitude
           lowestPrice
           rating
  startDate
   endDate
            state
   description
  clubId
  }
       clubs {
           id
           name
           city
           address
           latitude
           longitude
           logoImage
           rating
           priceRating
           state
       }
      }
   }
